{"tid":1450813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"812 1PM「警察還眼」 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:44.000Z","uid":149435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5464446649c06bd8e7ba04bcd6154674da35f6fc","tid":1450813,"uid":149435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是我們的責任，因為機場不夠大<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，要入健力士，留傳歷史<br />\n「黑警還眼 / an eye for an eye」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你入機場殺死所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️不沖禁區，不沖跑道‼️‼️<br />\n‼️‼️不沖禁區，不沖跑道‼️‼️<br />\n‼️‼️不沖禁區，不沖跑道‼️‼️<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WYypfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WYypfF.jpg&h=e48f5ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mE2hAG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mE2hAG.jpg&h=5e5c6f5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8daf89418eb2e02e2d63ddec752c7d91a7a889ed","tid":1450813,"uid":149435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218cbd8328802e327189f99aa83e514f957c1f6b","tid":1450813,"uid":149435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01077d15725a18647282ce5a28fddc159d5fe82","tid":1450813,"uid":283109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit